1 The object D and X are there. The object D is below and slightly to the right of the object X.
2 What is the relation of the agent X to the agent D?	upper-left	1
1 Q is below J at 7 o'clock.
2 What is the relation of the agent J to the agent Q?	upper-right	1
1 Z and L are horizontal and Z is to the right of L.
2 What is the relation of the agent L to the agent Z?	right	1
1 W is positioned right to S.
2 What is the relation of the agent W to the agent S?	right	1
1 O is placed at the upper right of D.
2 What is the relation of the agent O to the agent D?	upper-right	1
1 Y and W are in a vertical line with Y on top.
2 What is the relation of the agent Y to the agent W?	above	1
1 E is at the 6 o'clock position relative to L.
2 What is the relation of the agent L to the agent E?	above	1
1 A is slightly off center to the top left and W is slightly off center to the bottom right.
2 What is the relation of the agent W to the agent A?	lower-right	1
1 G is placed at the upper right of N.
2 What is the relation of the agent G to the agent N?	upper-right	1
1 The object W and U are there. The object U is above and slightly to the left of the object W.
2 What is the relation of the agent U to the agent W?	upper-left	1
